WEBVTT

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:09.000
Son Gohan!

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.000
For the sake of true justice...

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:16.000
There is no sin in fighting!

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Words and reasoning...

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:21.000
There are foes who can’t be reached by them!

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Unleash your spirit as it is—pure, like the light!

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:31.000
I know the pain you carry, but you no longer have to bear it alone!
